@inherits AdminComponentBase

<Overview3Cols>
    <Text1>
        <strong>AutoSnap</strong> automates the creation and management of VM/CT snapshots in Proxmox VE environments.<br />
        It provides scheduled snapshot jobs with configurable cron expressions, allowing precise control over when snapshots are created.<br />
        The module includes comprehensive retention management, automatically purging old snapshots based on defined policies.
    </Text1>

    <Text2>
        <strong>Scheduled Automation</strong>: Uses cron expressions for precise timing of snapshot creation across multiple VMs and containers.<br />
        <strong>Retention Policies</strong>: Automatically manages snapshot lifecycle with configurable keep counts and purging schedules.<br />
        <strong>Job Management</strong>: Provides comprehensive job tracking, error reporting, and timeline views for all snapshot operations.<br />
        <strong>Storage Efficiency</strong>: Prevents storage bloat through intelligent cleanup of expired snapshots.<br />
    </Text2>

    <Text3>
        <strong>Seamless Integration</strong>: Works natively with Proxmox VE API for reliable snapshot operations across cluster nodes.<br />
        <strong>Comprehensive Monitoring</strong>: Provides detailed status tracking, error logs, and dashboard widgets for operational visibility.<br />
        <strong>Enterprise Features</strong>: Supports multiple clusters, permission-based access control, and automated backup workflows.<br />
    </Text3>
</Overview3Cols>
